data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO NO FAULT OF THE SELLER. What an amazing property! This Easley gem abounds in country charm. Nestled in a cul-de-sac and sitting on a full acre lot, you will find all the allure of a full wrap around porch. The wrap around porch is sizable enough to house all your rocking chairs, a swing, and a dining table alike. Once you enter the home, you will find BRAND NEW flooring that was installed in November 2023. The living area features a gas log fireplace that is a perfect centerpiece for the living space. The kitchen features an exceptional amount of cabinetry and counter space with an oversized island. A brand-new dishwasher and other stainless-steel appliances including refrigerator make the kitchen the perfect space for entertaining. The first of two primary bedrooms is on the main level and features a private bathroom and a walk-in closet. Also, downstairs you will find the laundry room/half bath. Upstairs you will find 3 HUGE bedrooms, one of which can serve as a secondary master bedroom with another walk in closet and private bathroom. The other two bedrooms upstairs share a full hallway bath. If you are looking for that special property from a garage perspective this one is it! There is an attached 2 car garage that features a "bonus space" that is heated and cooled and currently used as an apartment. But, this space could be used in various ways- the previous homeowner used it for their business as a salon. It features a half bath and small kitchenette area. Around the corner, you will find a 1 car detached garage that has recently been framed for a room above as well. The stairway and the upstairs framing are in place. The fully fenced in backyard is flat, features some trees/foliage and a firepit area. I really can't say enough great things about this property and its potential! Make it your homeplace today!
